  "guide": {
    "palette": "Dark plum backgrounds (#2D1B33, #6B2D5B), warm gradient fills (gold #FFD93D → coral #FF6B6B, magenta #C850C0 → indigo #4158D0, blue #4158D0 → cyan #0ABDE3). Text: white headings, soft warm subtitles (#FFD4C4).",
